HOUSE BILL NO. 387
BY REPRESENTATIVE GADBERRY
1 AN ACT
2 To amend and reenact R.S. 40:1574.1(C)(1), relative to the practice of professional
3 engineering and land surveying; to provide for plan review procedures by the state
4 fire marshal; and to provide for related matters.
5 Be it enacted by the Legislature of Louisiana:
6 Section 1. R.S. 40:1574.1(C)(1) is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
7 §1574.1. Costs of handling plans
8 * * *
9 C.(1) In the event that plans do not appear to the fire marshal to satisfactorily
10 comply with the laws, regulations, and codes of Louisiana and the regulations of the
11 state fire marshal, the state fire marshal shall furnish a letter to the party submitting
12 the plans which shall list the particular requirements of the state fire marshal which
13 must be met before the plans can be stamped "Reviewed" and before construction
14 or renovation or remodeling can begin. However, where plans for projects are
15 submitted in violation of R.S. 37:155(A)(4) or R.S. 37:701(I), no list of requirements
16 shall be provided.
